name: Garter belts
description:
If you'd like to support me and do more:
https://ko-fi.com/edgonkofi - commissions open!
If you're looking for a >>LoRA Making Tutorial<<

GARTER BELTS

Truly, garter belts are a fine invention. They are, in my opinion, the pinnacle of lingerie and a proof that man wants nothing more than to beautify the woman.

Garter belts are therefore a symbol of love, a symbol of harmony between the two sexes. Men will make or buy a beautiful garter belt for their spouse, and women will don the garter belt and unveil it in front of their man like a magician taking out a rabbit out of his hat in front of a child with stars in his eyes and a smile on his face!

Today, I bring you this beautiful symbol of love and harmony in LoRA format.

Spread the love, and have fun!

ADDITIONAL INFORMATION AND BEST PRACTICES:

Since garter belts are very intricate and complex, I strongly suggest you take my prompts, use them as a base, and create the garter belt that will make you melt!
